textBeforeTable: G101 Prospect Price Distance (KM) Dep. Time - Arr. Time Arrival City Train No. Trains to & from Xuzhou Xuzhou is known as one of the most important rail transport hubs of China. It is located in northwestern Jiangsu Province, with Henan to the west, Shandong to the north, and Shanghai to the south. It is at the intersection of the Beijing-Shanghai Railway, the Longhai Railway, the Beijing-Shanghai High-speed Railway, and the Xuzhou-Lanzhou High-speed Railway being constructed. This marks the rail crossroads connecting eastern, western, northern, and southern provinces and cities in China. Every day, the railway stations in Xuzhou transfer numerous passengers from all corners of the country. Please see our Xuzhou train schedule for more information. The Xuzhou train schedule provides information on trains going to eastern, western, northern, and southern provinces and cities in China.
